- create/delete activities
- add/delete kids

- schedule activities
    - create a one-time schedule
        - choose a date
    - create a recurrent schedule
        - start and end date
        - weekly or monthly
            - weekly: which days of the week
            - monthly:
                - which day of the month
                - which weeks of the month + which days of the week

        - add an exception to a recurrent schedule
            - add a cancellation
            - add a rescheduling

- register kids to activities
